{"tid":1886093,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"（今日上庭）手足9月21日被捕及還押至今150日","createTime":"2020-02-18T17:21:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-18T17:49:21.000Z","uid":239516,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"c33ef486801c0342d371047908bb394b31c90f25","tid":1886093,"uid":239516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T17:21:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/涉藏打火機燃料等-理大生不認罪-指警插贓嫁禍-還押明年開審/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E6%B6%89%E8%97%8F%E6%89%93%E7%81%AB%E6%A9%9F%E7%87%83%E6%96%99%E7%AD%89-%E7%90%86%E5%A4%A7%E7%94%9F%E4%B8%8D%E8%AA%8D%E7%BD%AA-%E6%8C%87%E8%AD%A6%E6%8F%92%E8%B4%93%E5%AB%81%E7%A6%8D-%E9%82%84%E6%8A%BC%E6%98%8E%E5%B9%B4%E9%96%8B%E5%AF%A9%2F&d=WZLdF6k3LRQ%2Bb7h5E4OoDpuyGkzLGvEkvhYecc72uXM%3D&h=bbd59b97\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E6%B6%89%E8%97%8F%E6%89%93%E7%81%AB%E6%A9%9F%E7%87%83%E6%96%99%E7%AD%89-%E7%90%86%E5%A4%A7%E7%94%9F%E4%B8%8D%E8%AA%8D%E7%BD%AA-%E6%8C%87%E8%AD%A6%E6%8F%92%E8%B4%93%E5%AB%81%E7%A6%8D-%E9%82%84%E6%8A%BC%E6%98%8E%E5%B9%B4%E9%96%8B%E5%AF%A9%2F&h=111399ac\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/涉藏打火機燃料等-理大生不認罪-指警插贓嫁禍-還押明年開審/</a>"},{"pid":"5b4452720f2bea3991d1d01e1526bc00d81a9782","tid":1886093,"uid":325840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T17:22:16.000Z","msg":"有手足還押150天聽日上庭<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1885989\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1885989</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"20f78b1b2076afcc5d0d97399cc00dd2fe7bc774","tid":1886093,"uid":239516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T17:22:30.000Z","msg":"逾百市民於9月21日圍堵旺角警署，一名理大學生在警方驅散期間，涉嫌被搜出打火機燃料、塞有布料的玻璃樽等物品被落案起訴，今（2日）在西九龍裁判法院否認一項「在公眾地方管有攻擊性武器」罪。案件排期於下年1月2日開審，預計審期為2日，辯方指控警方插贓嫁禍，表明會就此作爭議。被告沒有保釋申請，需繼續還押。<br />\n<br />\n被告吳俊偉 （22歲，學生）被控於今年9月21日，在旺角彌敦道及太子道西交界的公眾地方，無合法權限或合理辯解而攜有攻擊性武器，即一個玻璃樽（樽口塞有一塊布）、一罐打火機燃料及一把鎚仔。"},{"pid":"10574512e4e9c86cb4ebb612c0bea674b8ecbee1","tid":1886093,"uid":239516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T17:23:25.000Z","msg":"【#上庭聲援 - 2 月 1 9 日 星期三】<br />\n［旁聽須知］［交通資訊］<br />\n［疫症期間安排］<br />\n［法院延期公告］<br />\n<br />\n►--- 09:30 am ---◄ <br />\n🏛西 九 龍 裁 判 法 院 4 樓 1 庭<br />\n👨🏻&zwj;⚖️#羅德泉主任裁判官<br />\n👥李,利(22-25)🛑已還押6天 保釋覆核（#20200101旺角 襲警:便衣警員A；杜官庭上指『點解唔告埋非法集結』）<br />\n👤埃及籍被告(35)🛑已還押6天 保釋覆核（#1006旺角 有意圖而傷人:私了）<br />\n👥 2名被告 #新案件（#20200217天水圍 新案件詳情未知）<br />\n<br />\n🏛西 九 龍 裁 判 法 院 4 樓 3 庭<br />\n👩🏻&zwj;⚖️#香淑嫻裁判官<br />\n👥李(32)🛑已還押25天 保釋覆核 （#20200122屯門 管有攻擊性武器:汽油彈和鐳射筆）<br />\n<br />\n►--- 02:30 pm ---◄ <br />\n🏛西 九 龍 裁 判 法 院 4 樓 1 庭<br />\n👩🏻&zwj;⚖️#劉綺雲裁判官<br />\n👤吳(22)🛑已還押150天 保釋覆核（#0921旺角 管有攻擊性武器:汽油彈和鎚仔）<br />\n<br />\n或有新案件提堂，請留意本頻聲援公告"},{"pid":"9279d1c54a93e6f7848b4ae01325c8702b2bd0e8","tid":1886093,"uid":235370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T17:25:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3448e9d25e83f94d56b71536ab578a3b80630671","tid":1886093,"uid":239516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T17:26:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1316b165e62fac6e525d1e7254bbc187ee60dcea","tid":1886093,"uid":239516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T17:27:52.000Z","msg":"果然連登真係曬尻氣"},{"pid":"2fc45d517d99eec99a19422d64c0cecb44d0e111","tid":1886093,"uid":44978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T17:31:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/